to find clues that match

I was just trying to tie everything together to one person, waiting for my team to introduce new clues and putting things together based on them.

Honestly I just went with my gut which was probably a mistake. I trusted the information I saw first and then tried to corroborate it with further evidence.
I was trying to gather clues that seemed to fit together the best with mostly the helo of just one of the other players who seemed the smartest.
